## Project Overview
{{.Description}}

## Tech Stack
- **Language**: Ruby 3.3
- **Framework**: Ruby on Rails 8.0
- **Database**: PostgreSQL 17 (via Docker)
- **ORM**: Active Record
- **Web Server**: Puma

## Project Structure
- `app/controllers/` - Action controllers
- `app/models/` - Active Record models
- `app/views/` - View templates (ERB)
- `config/` - Configuration files
- `config/routes.rb` - Route definitions
- `db/migrate/` - Database migrations
- `test/` - Minitest test suite
- `docs/supporting/` - Supporting documentation

## Development Commands
```bash
make start    # Start Docker Compose stack
make stop     # Stop all services
make test     # Run tests
make migrate  # Run migrations
make shell    # Rails console
make bash     # Shell into container
make routes   # Show routes
```

## Conventions
- Follow Rails conventions (MVC, RESTful routes, Active Record)
- Models in `app/models/`, controllers in `app/controllers/`
- Use Rails generators for scaffolding
- Database config in `config/database.yml`
- Environment config via ENV variables
- Use strong parameters for mass assignment protection
